{"text_id":254001,"tokens":["The"," implementation"," of"," a"," new"," school"," policy"," that"," mandates"," maintaining"," a"," grade"," B"," average"," for"," participation"," in"," sports"," and"," extracurricular"," activities"," is"," a"," proposition"," that"," aims"," to"," elevate"," academic"," achievements"," and"," incul","cate"," a"," culture"," of"," excellence"," among"," students","."," This"," essay"," discusses"," the"," potential"," advantages"," and"," disadvantages"," of"," such"," a"," policy",","," along"," with"," recommendations"," to"," balance"," its"," prospective"," impact",".","\n","Advoc","ates"," of"," the"," policy"," argue"," that"," it"," would"," serve"," as"," an"," incentive"," for"," students"," to"," prioritize"," their"," studies"," and"," strive"," for"," higher"," academic"," performance","."," Indeed",","," requiring"," a"," B"," average"," could"," foster"," a"," sense"," of"," responsibility"," and"," time"," management",","," encouraging"," students"," to"," allocate"," appropriate"," time"," to"," their"," studies"," while"," engaging"," in"," non","-","academic"," pursuits","."," Furthermore",","," integrating"," academic"," and"," extracurricular"," requirements"," helps"," prepare"," students"," for"," the"," professional"," world"," where"," multitasking"," and"," maintaining"," a"," balanced"," skill"," set"," are"," often"," necessary",".","\n","Additionally",","," this"," policy"," could"," inspire"," students"," to"," reach"," for"," excellence"," not"," only"," in"," their"," academic"," pursuits"," but"," also"," in"," their"," personal"," development","."," It"," sends"," a"," clear"," message"," that"," educational"," institutions"," value"," holistic"," development","\u2014","where"," both"," mental"," acuity"," and"," physical"," prowess"," are"," recognized"," as"," corner","stones"," of"," a"," well","-","rounded"," character",".","\n","However",","," the"," proposed"," policy"," is"," not"," without"," its"," drawbacks","."," There"," is"," a"," concern"," that"," it"," may"," disproportion","ately"," impact"," students"," who"," struggle"," academically",","," potentially"," due"," to"," socio","-","economic"," backgrounds"," or"," learning"," difficulties","."," Such"," students"," could"," be"," unfairly"," denied"," the"," enrichment"," that"," sports"," and"," extracurricular"," activities"," provide",","," which"," can"," include"," essential"," life"," skills"," such"," as"," teamwork",","," communication",","," and"," resilience",".","\n","To"," mitigate"," negatives"," and"," maximize"," positives",","," I"," recommend"," a"," supportive"," and"," inclusive"," approach"," to"," implementing"," this"," policy","."," Schools"," should"," provide"," additional"," tutoring"," and"," mentorship"," to"," help"," students"," who"," are"," on"," the"," cusp"," of"," meeting"," academic"," thresholds","."," Moreover",","," the"," policy"," could"," be"," more"," flexible",","," allowing"," probation","ary"," periods"," where"," students"," can"," still"," participate"," in"," activities"," while"," receiving"," academic"," support",".","\n","Lastly",","," the"," initiative"," would"," benefit"," from"," continuous"," assessment"," and"," review"," to"," ensure"," it"," aligns"," with"," its"," objectives"," and"," does"," not"," unintentionally"," exclude"," or"," demo","tivate"," students","."," By"," investing"," in"," support"," systems"," and"," fostering"," an"," environment"," where"," every"," student"," is"," given"," an"," opportunity"," to"," succeed",","," the"," policy"," has"," the"," potential"," to"," cultivate"," an"," environment"," wherein"," academic"," and"," extra","-","curricular"," excellence"," work"," hand","-","in","-","hand"," to"," produce"," future"," leaders"," and"," responsible"," citizens","."],"sub_source":"outfox","model":"gpt-3.5-turbo","label":1}